      "content": "I see. So you're essentially saying that the \"homogenous\" past was what maintained that stability. To follow that logic, does it mean that a society's ability to function effectively is tied to its ethnic or cultural uniformity? Like, is there an inherent incompatibility between these traditional Western frameworks and the values brought in by these rising minority populations?",
